## 4. THRESHOLDS E DECISES

### 4.1 Limites Configurveis

```yaml
# neocortex_config.yaml (seo confidence_review)
confidence_review:
  threshold_auto: 80      # 80  autoapprove
  threshold_reject: 50    # <50  reject
  weights:                # pesos opcionais por validador
    naming: 1.5
    atomic_locks: 2.0     # locks tm peso maior
    py_compile: 1.0
    ssot_update: 1.2
    barriers: 1.3
    yaml_validity: 1.0
    handoff_completeness: 1.0
  auto_update_ssot: true  # se SSOT validador falhar, atualiza automaticamente?
```

### 4.2 Fluxo de Deciso

```
1. Handoff gerado (status: PENDING_REVIEW)
2. ConfidenceReviewService avalia  score 0100
3. Deciso:
   - Score 80  status: APPROVED, ticket: DONE
   - Score <50  status: REJECTED, ticket: AVAILABLE (retorna  fila)
   - Score 5079  status: MANUAL_REVIEW, aguarda T0
4. Notificao (opcional)  EventBus, log, dashboard
```

### 4.3 Exemplos

| Score | Deciso | Cenrio tpico |
|---|---|---|
| 92 | APPROVED | Todos os validadores passaram com alta pontuao |
| 65 | MANUAL_REVIEW | SSOT no atualizado (score 40), mas resto ok |
| 30 | REJECTED | Arquivo @LOCK modificado (score 0) + naming incorreto |

